-- Travelodge Ltd. Chairman Keith Hamill Quits, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-07-15T09:14:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/travelodge-ltd-chairman-keith-hamill-quits-sunday-times-says.html
Travelodge Ltd. Chairman Keith Hamill has quit his role at the U.K. budget hotel chain, the
 Sunday Times  reported without saying where it got the
information.  The company declined to comment, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
